Reasoning: The paper deals with a multi-level MIMO relaying system and analyzes the asymptotic mutual information and optimal precoding strategy. This falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of free probability theory and the analysis of channel correlation matrices suggest that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of signal processing (cs.SI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper deals with communication systems and networks, which could also place it under the sub-category of computer communications (cs.COM).
